AuraDescription_lang: Darkness envelops you every $s1 kills, causing you to be completely unable to view your surroundings. While under this effect, your damage and healing done is increased by $341375s2% and your movement speed is increased by $341375s3%. This effect is only removed when you kill $s2 more enemies.
